== 票房反應 ==
2006年10月，此片的反應不一。[[路透社|路透社]]形容此片「視覺豐富」、「劇情緊湊」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20070104%2FREVIEWS%2F701040301%2F1023 |title=Sun Times review |accessdate=2020-09-22 |archive-date=2009-12-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5lw3V5LrH?url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20070104%2FREVIEWS%2F701040301%2F1023 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]網站上，網友投票的比例各半<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfume_the_story_of_a_murderer/ |title=Rotten Tomatoes review |accessdate=2008-09-09 |archive-date=2008-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913191009/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfume_the_story_of_a_murderer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

此片在[[歐洲|歐洲]]有驚人的票房表現，全球有一億美元的票房。然而，片商認為此片在[[北美|北美]]並不會有好的票房，因此只在某些[[電影院|電影院]]上映，票房為2,223,293美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=perfume.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-09-09 |archive-date=2008-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210045541/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=perfume.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

